<h2 class="bold font-l">Tritannus</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Tritannus is unable to apologize for what he had done, only feeling sorry that he didn't destroy everything when he had the chance. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>The Unrepentant</span> </h3>
